data.description: Chicago Bungalow in the Greater Grand Crossing Neighborhood.  True investor special.  The property will need a full gut rehab.   The house has two bedrooms upstairs and one in the basement.  One bathroom upstairs and a half bath in the basement.  The basement family room runs the full length of the house. The Basement also has a laundry and additional storage.  There is a stairwell to the attic and it is ready to be dormered and made into additional living space.  This house is unique because it has an enclosed front and back porches.  There is a very nice size backyard and a two car garage.   The garage is in great need of repair.  Property to be sold as-is.  No survey to be provided.  Highest and best called for by 5pm on Saturday October 21st.
